VITE_COGNITO_USER_POOL_ID=your-user-pool-id
VITE_COGNITO_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id
VITE_COGNITO_DOMAIN=your-cognito-domain.auth.region.amazoncognito.com
VITE_COGNITO_REDIRECT_SIGN_IN=http://localhost:3000
VITE_COGNITO_REDIRECT_SIGN_OUT=http://localhost:3000

# === ソーシャルログインプロバイダー設定 ===
# 以下の各プロバイダーを設定した後、AWS Cognito User PoolでIDプロバイダーとして追加する必要があります

# Google OAuth Configuration
# 1. Google Cloud Console (https://console.cloud.google.com/) でプロジェクトを作成
# 2. APIs & Services > Credentials > Create Credentials > OAuth 2.0 Client ID
# 3. 承認済みのJavaScript生成元: http://localhost:3000
# 4. 承認済みのリダイレクトURI: https://your-cognito-domain.auth.region.amazoncognito.com/oauth2/idpresponse
# 5. Client IDとClient Secretをメモ
# 6. AWS Cognito > User Pools > Sign-in experience > Add identity provider > Google

# Facebook OAuth Configuration
# 1. Facebook for Developers (https://developers.facebook.com/) でアプリを作成
# 2. 設定 > 基本設定 からApp IDとApp Secretを取得
# 3. Facebook Login > 設定 で以下を設定:
#    - 有効なOAuthリダイレクトURI: https://your-cognito-domain.auth.region.amazoncognito.com/oauth2/idpresponse
# 4. AWS Cognito > User Pools > Sign-in experience > Add identity provider > Facebook

# LINE OAuth Configuration
# 1. LINE Developers Console (https://developers.line.biz/) でチャネルを作成
# 2. チャネル基本設定からChannel IDとChannel Secretを取得
# 3. LINE Login設定:
#    - Callback URL: https://your-cognito-domain.auth.region.amazoncognito.com/oauth2/idpresponse
# 4. AWS Cognito > User Pools > Sign-in experience > Add identity provider > OpenID Connect
#    - Provider name: LINE
#    - Client ID: LINE Channel ID
#    - Client secret: LINE Channel Secret
#    - Authorize scope: openid profile email
#    - Issuer: https://access.line.me
#    - Authorization endpoint: https://access.line.me/oauth2/v2.1/authorize
#    - Token endpoint: https://api.line.me/oauth2/v2.1/token
#    - Userinfo endpoint: https://api.line.me/v2/profile
#    - Jwks uri: https://api.line.me/oauth2/v2.1/certs
